strings.Value: "Yeah, haven't done that much in quite a while..."
"I feel like I've been carrying bricks all day... And I thought I'd never be a slave again, ha, ha!"
"Don't worry about him. He's a big boy. He can take care of himself."
"And yet so many have it worse than we!"
"You don't say! But all the beautiful scenery, exciting events, the people we meet... All this is more than enough reward for our struggles! Right, friends?"
"On such days I'm glad the dead feel nothing... including fatigue."
